  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>REDtech</span> <span>2026-03-10 18:03</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">上海</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f6c7a070&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FP9Hs04VFGRnt6hDkrPIUNEzyfzic7Co817G0sqAbAT0ibQggGmfl900ickwicBXpDquEgSfjYbMhKkLqARqOTcicv0S9Uiamyyv4wibYlu3vp2tObk%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>Vision-R1重磅登场：以 200K 条无人工标注的高质量多模态 CoT 冷启动数据打底，融合 GRPO 与渐进式思维抑制训练（PTST），有效解决多模态大模型“过度思考”难题，显著激发复杂推理能力。</p>\n  <div style=\"font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 7px;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1a6743ac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FP9Hs04VFGRnRibYiaqG1xYliaYVXj4bv6Avw2O8HAoBO9icCm0SbOu18xovqgeE8pUxDLuU1rJGJ7gVloGtpeTvlWMAmibAQrmd9G8kUnfLVAmPM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-left-color: rgba(160, 160, 160, 0.32);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 14px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 5px 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Vision-R1 重磅登场：以 200K 条无人工标注的高质量多模态 CoT 冷启动数据打底，融合 GRPO 与渐进式思维抑制训练（PTST），有效解决多模态大模型“过度思考”难题，显著激发复杂推理能力。 7B 模型在 MathVista 达 73.5%，效果接近 OpenAI O1。</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.3268733850129199\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"774\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=74924fb2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FpawZofA4fxNfw3txUq9Z3WHr7bhH6R3y820DEibDoahAzSxcLNHbGiaso43Oia2wJibI01xicnOpj67Y1KGSRzJTcho8Aiak3lI7EOoY5hWQ60bKw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39903846153846156\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"832\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c7dea4d3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FpawZofA4fxPZM9BjN3QVx1v29kJibH8HeQrE6Za1wib8kLb3bicdUaGPtMiayVJCyfleP76oTC3VXvDxQk4R0jzhziaeChTXmbJFMKtYEdMWibNVg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-left-color: rgba(160, 160, 160, 0.32);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 14px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 5px 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Vision-R1: Incentivizing Reasoning Capability in Multimodal Large Language Models</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2503.06749\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2503.06749</a></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.1651376146788991\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"872\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8c4e6dac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FpawZofA4fxPbZ5Jme2eRrQ85AEiatIhAnCU2FvmhC5PjO4fHUX3jdkQxykewoNWtNu3AkQ4rRsA2CD5Fqs81L88KQ8eWrNibliaL82NNH5bianA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在通向通用人工智能（Artificial General Intelligence, AGI）的道路上，复杂推理能力始终是大语言模型（Large Language Models, LLMs）的重要瓶颈，而这一挑战在引入视觉模态后变得更为艰巨。这存在以下几个问题：</span></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">大语言模型推理火热，但多模态推理仍是短板</span></strong></span></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">近年来，纯文本领域推理方法（如“链式思考”、Tree-of-Thought 等）发展迅速，证明了在文本任务中，通过显式的多步推理，可极大提升模型在复杂问题上的表现。然而，这些方法大多只聚焦在文本输入上，很少考虑视觉信息。多模态大模型若只停留在“根据图像简单识别+给出答案”，常常难以在高难度推理场景（如数学场景的图文结合推理、几何题带图解等）表现优异。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">直接用强化学习在多模态模型上激发“自发思考”并不容易</span></strong></span></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在纯文本模型上，已有工作（如 DeepSeek-R1）表明，利用强化学习去激发模型自我生成更复杂的推理链，确实有效。但想直接将这种强化学习方法“照搬”到多模态大模型，会面临数据稀缺、模型过度胡乱生成长推理链等问题，导致效果不佳。因此，需要一个辅助的冷启动初始化步骤来帮助模型先学会“如何思考”，然后再进行强化学习，以提升推理过程的正确性与稳健性。</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 25px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.15807174887892378\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"892\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=055b4452&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRkQvlWicZkBD0Fg09DViapMDEQstUOXq5UAgL8cCdhLRlWJw34CTjWP9ys9qWCSFSXFf4Mdq6OuWZMia31hAgJumSUEaWDuJSEuoY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8293269230769231\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"832\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54656072&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRmC7Gq0eJpPo6uCPXZ6objae9438rUcbKyibbYMibY1BgaRrqZr1kickOib3SQZic10h0RY0tRvqf3cDjzkL9TT60WeznCT5Rg7OhrQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin: 20px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">直接强化学习难以激发推理能力</span></span></strong></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文最先尝试了一个直觉做法：在没任何预热的情况下，直接对多模态模型进行强化学习训练，企图让模型自发生成复杂的推理过程。结果发现，模型难以从零开始形成准确且复杂的推理链，往往一味追求“产出长推理”却忽视了正确性，性能难以获得提升。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">冷启动面临高质量数据匮乏</span></span></strong></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">想要先做冷启动进行预热，想让多模态模型先学会“像人一样思考”，需要兼具视觉、语言乃至数学场景下的复杂推理示例，但纯人工大规模标注成本非常高。如何在极少或无人工干预的情况下，获得高质量、多样化的多模态推理数据，也是一个难题。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">存在“过度思考”优化难题</span></span></strong></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果在多模态模型上先通过冷启动学到一些复杂的推理模式，再做强化学习时，会出现另一类问题：模型往往倾向于生成过长的思考过程，其中充斥着错误或冗余的步骤，这种“思考过度”会使得训练过程变得不稳定，难以成功优化到正确且高效的推理模式。</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 30px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15291529152915292\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"909\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3fdb31ec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRkG5yQg7shfjzX1AYAYE16Wv2YFkpQZPTk979ibbwicBSricZSzplOfrJoKVhCe5C526HOoyq7Qy05mYQBvP6kefGp1Tp08nmJm2I%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin: 20px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们的研究揭示了当前两大核心瓶颈：</span></p>\n     <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据之困</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：高质量多模态思维链数据极度稀缺，人工标注成本高昂且难以捕捉真实思维动态，这导致了冷启动数据难以获得的问题。</span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">优化之难</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：直接对冷启动后的多模态大模型使用强化学习（RL）训练会导致“过度思考优化问题 （Overthink Optimization Problem）”，即模型在早期训练时无法激活内生复杂推理能力，而长时间训练后又倾向于生成冗余重复的推理过程，这使得多模态大模型的泛化能力难以强化。</span></p>\n      </li>\n     </ol>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于此，我们提出了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Vision-R1&nbsp;</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">多模态推理大模型，以系统性创新突破了上述挑战。</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 20px 0px 10px;transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-left-color: rgb(12, 12, 12);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 14px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(12, 12, 12);padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">无监督高质量思维链数据生成</span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.506426735218509\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"778\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=967b193f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRnEwaCXnafOWKgguLfQcUzXqTLyqkibzYCQOjXVvp2ZtlJVqmGb3nVRnOOMBpTSNOPOibSs40mdl5K8QCExm0bIxHSFlibKbWYeko%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7942857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"700\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=77ba64d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRlm3YDGB1icVz24CvGFBqeR2DMLRAUTfmbzrz0iaFyKZQiaWPia1K3cpiaMFMiczUO1wcJRIYrXRzQkBHxVf6a2d0UjyjAOeFLPs9uoY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin: 20px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">团队创新性地提出了</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">模态桥接（Modality Bridging）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">方法，首次实现多模态 CoT 数据的自动化构造流水线：</span></p>\n     <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">模态桥接</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：利用现有多模态大模型从图文对中生成含视觉描述的结构化“伪推理链”，再将问题对和\"伪推理链\"交给多模态大模型生成足够详细的文本描述，巧妙的将图片信息转变为文本信息以可以被 DeepSeek-R1 所捕捉。如图3所示，这一方式避免了描述信息不足导致 DeepSeek-R1 无法做出正确的推理。</span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">高质量思维链获取</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：将第一步产生的足够详细的文本描述后输入 DeepSeek-R1 提取高质量 CoT。</span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">后处理规则过滤</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：基于规则进行数据后处理，进一步提升质量。</span></p>\n      </li>\n     </ul>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如上图所示，该流水线产出 200K 高质量多模态 CoT 数据集&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Vision-R1-cold</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，其推理步骤呈现人类特有的</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“质疑反思”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的逻辑推理思考范式。该数据被用于进行 Vision-R1 的冷启动，使模型先学习复杂思考的形式。</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 20px 0px 10px;transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-left-color: rgb(12, 12, 12);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 14px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(12, 12, 12);padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">渐进式思维优化</span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.40617283950617283\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"810\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d5ebb93f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRluJFHVsN7OHD3Ts9ibaDCgRTAtMukGxIqOek75HqkibicIs2e88wUQlqqgv9NvFsu8oSyRO7ZIuRQxicOo4qIlVBNA2CrbC5XSFjY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin: 20px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对冷启动后续强化学习训练中的过度思考问题，创新性地提出</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">渐进式思维抑制训练</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">（Progressive Thinking Suppression Training, PTST）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">与硬格式结果奖励函数</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">（Hard Formatting Result Reward Function, HFRRF）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n     <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">PTST 机制</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：如上图所示，仿照人类认知发展规律，在训练初期约束推理过程长度，使模型优先内化核心推理逻辑，学会正确的思考方式，再逐步扩展推理长度，提升复杂推理能力。</span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">HFRRF 优化 GRPO</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：采用与 DeepSeek-R1 相同的分组相对策略优化（Group Relative Policy Optimization）的强化学习方法，并通过硬格式结果奖励（即同时满足格式正确和答案正确才可以获得奖励）引导模型学习正确推理，形成\"关键节点验证\"的推理范式。</span></p>\n      </li>\n     </ul>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">上述策略使 7B 参数的 Vision-R1 在 10K RL 训练数据集上实现推理能力大幅增强，其推理效率较基线有着显著提升。</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 20px 0px 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1602787456445993\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"861\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=908d6d9a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRnKuUIedc4J6qnbZzoibYmicxZyyXOwfP5PlH32iaC59ZpRQdRNP1v9QhXBHnXiawxrIlOttZ1LySzOR73qicgibe1VwzS6ImnbxLv2c%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin: 20px 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Vision-R1 的突破性不仅体现在方法创新上，更在系统化实验中获得了严谨验证。我们从三大维度来揭示其认知推理能力跃迁的内在机制：</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 20px 0px 10px;transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-left-color: rgb(12, 12, 12);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 14px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(12, 12, 12);padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">数学推理：7B模型的\"逆袭时刻\"</span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.7596153846153846\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"832\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4c68bb15&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRmQumrupibRiblbPebK5VP4I4hyicSjpdb4xc5ptEcfelnzxQYGGJyBzYgJw9vBQqXt4YYQuPY39uUAeSiaUG1ISsmH6POSluDp32g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如上表所示，Vision-R1-7B 在 MathVista 基准测试中取得 73.5% 的准确率，与 OpenAI O1 的差距缩小至 0.4%——这意味着仅用 7B 参数量即可比肩顶尖商业模型的数学推理水平。当 scaling 到 32B/72B 尺寸模型和更多数据，Vision-R1 在 scaling 中表现突出。更值得关注的是：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在MathVista的几何推理（Geometry Reasoning, GEO）、算术推理（Algebraic Reasoning, ALG）、几何问题求解（Geometry Problem Solving, GPS）等子任务中，Vision-R1-7B 以 80.3%、79.0%、83.2% 的准确率全面超越基座模型 Qwen-2.5-VL-7B。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;text-size-adjust: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 MathVerse 与 MM-Math 基准上，Vision-R1-7B 的 MM-Math 成绩仅次于参数量10倍的 Qwen-2.5-VL-72B。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-left-color: rgb(12, 12, 12);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 14px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(12, 12, 12);padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">思维链质量：揭开200K数据集的认知密码</span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.3125\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"832\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7c603112&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRkgyQmZH0SJAfgTe6vDWXz02ofa8UZoKdBxtRP9nGeVmXzvvoYnjMUNadYSwJmRF9chcNxZ9jMCicVTcico5NNMSUIlcI3nY5zkg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.28846153846153844\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"832\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9ec69d64&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRmwPZOpBMdHYxnInmXSwaEvVBmibticz0k3YDrBpp9RwmsgSYnaHa2OsWc7Pd4ibOyPiaNLBz89banVaZ00NkAbNdlr8PdheDVYMfw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为评估 Vision-R1-cold 数据集的质量，团队进行了数据质量分析：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">对比 Mulberry (260K)、llava-cot (100K) 等数据集，Vision-R1-cold (200K) 的质疑（Questioning）、反思（Reflection）、检验（Inspection）等认知要素出现频率提升3-5倍（见表2）。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于 Llama-3.2-11B-V-Instruct 的基座模型对比实验显示，使用 Vision-R1-cold 微调的模型在通用和数学 Benchmark 上相较于传统的“伪 CoT”数据集都实现了大幅的领先，证明其数据质量以及思维链结构更符合人类推理模式。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-left-color: rgb(12, 12, 12);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 14px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(12, 12, 12);padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">训练动力学：PTST 如何破解\"过度思考\"困局</span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过可视化强化学习训练过程，我们发现：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">思维压缩效应</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：应用 PTST 策略后，模型在初期训练阶段压缩了思考过程长度，而准确率有显著提升。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">渐进泛化能力</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：随着训练推进，模型在保持核心推理逻辑的同时，鼓励模型进行复杂推理，逐步将思考长度扩展，最后做到具有复杂思维能力的同时，正确做出推理。</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 20px 0px 10px;transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-left-color: rgb(12, 12, 12);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 14px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(12, 12, 12);padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">消融实验：冷启动+强化学习+PTST 的协同效应</span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5297619047619048\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"672\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f07a293d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRnAhjJGpVBpkibiaGib5AAxHO7ODiav1qhVpx4xTHZj0CVtAXFCWRrjSGdrLWGN1ZC3X77WfMo6NQ1hCTZRNnTTPm16S7af0MCc3DY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为验证框架各组件贡献，我们对比了四种训练策略（见上表）：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Vision-R1-Zero</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（纯强化训练）：因缺乏高质量初始化数据，生成的思维链长度不足且结构简单，复杂任务准确率受限。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Vision-R1-CI</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（仅冷启动）：虽能生成长推理链，但冗余错误步骤占比较高，导致整体性能下降。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Vision-R1-Long</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（冷启动+强化学习，无 PTST ）：直接优化较为困难，准确率波动幅度较大。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Vision-R1</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（冷启动+强化学习+PTST）：通过 PTST 策略动态调节推理深度，在做到复杂推理的情况下，保证推理准确率。</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">实验证明：冷启动提供“认知种子”，PTST 实现“思维修剪”，二者协同使模型获得最优的推理效率-准确性平衡。这一发现为多模态大模型的强化训练提供了全新范式。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.2668269230769231\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"832\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=709cef89&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRmhZlc0ribrKibib889fo7dYQWzPfB1R0lpvESkJ5XUrjge8SVKUIAn0R0LCLoOMsdbrDLbeCUZ2QlaGApKibmHicYq6GNmFOkgcjGc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为验证 PTST 的作用，我们详细对比了几种训练策略。实验表明，Vision-R1 的渐进训练取得了最佳的效果，这一策略简单且有效。</span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15091863517060367\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"762\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c678de48&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRl9MT6PI3nY5SfIAoWWmKh585dglSnq83AtiadrkMicAECJiaYib1z346F3bgVIYJqgrSkm4jGKWbJicexbShVF186AqKofFXEu2Ueo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin: 20px 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">方法创新</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：首创无监督多模态思维链生成与渐进式思维抑制训练（PTST），突破传统依赖人工标注数据与直接强化学习的双重瓶颈，实现复杂推理能力的自我涌现。</span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">性能突破</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：仅 7B 参数的模型在数学推理任务中比肩 70B+级商业模型，验证“小模型+优算法”可超越参数规模限制。当 scaling 模型参数和数据规模，均取得显著的提升，方法的泛化性显著。</span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">关键机制设计</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：冷启动+强化学习+PTST 协同作用，有效平衡了推理链复杂度与准确性，解决“不思考”和“过思考”的问题。</span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据生产革命</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：自动化构建 200K 高质量 CoT 数据集，首次实现多模态推理认知数据的规模化生产，大量降低成本。</span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">范式影响</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：推动多模态模型从“感知再现”迈向“思维涌现”，为通用人工智能的认知架构演进提供新路径。</span></p>\n      </li>\n     </ul>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">启示录</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：当机器开始学会在视觉认知中自我质疑、动态修正，我们正见证着多模态智能从“感知再现”走向“思维涌现”的历史性拐点。Vision-R1 的突破预示着：通用人工智能的拼图上，又一块关键组件已悄然就位。</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 25px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.141287284144427\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"637\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=847c6024&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FP9Hs04VFGRnCYnicHWu1c2ALCaTMNwTFW0oflet0J8SeAo7k43IhGBKJCZibSp15iclHhvzqv799gHYkhxlkIVwhOpphI7u0owbLSEFvrRH0aM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <grammarly-extension style=\"top: 0px;left: 0px;pointer-events: none;\"></grammarly-extension><grammarly-extension style=\"top: 0px;left: 0px;pointer-events: none;\"></grammarly-extension>\n    <div style=\"margin: 12px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">小红书大模型团队招人啦～</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">招聘大模型算法工程师/算法专家，预训练、SFT、RL、数据&amp;评测、AI Infra，有相关实习经验、顶会论文、开源项目、竞赛奖项获得者优先，地点：北京/上海/杭州，浓厚的技术氛围，部分团队工作：业务统一后训练 RedOne/RedOne 2.0，小红书翻译 RedTrans，多模态推理 Vision-R1，多模态 Vision-DeepResearch，扩散大语言模型 RedLLM，情感陪聊 iPET等，社招/校招/实习均可。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">投递邮箱：</span></p>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">caoshaosheng@xiaohongshu.com</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 0px 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.2777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080